{"tid":1347983,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"比人踩到上心口喇 仲忍？","createTime":"2019-07-22T07:13:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T09:47:38.000Z","uid":96536,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f632211b56af84e54ae8e05bb33a3ff977e0fade","tid":1347983,"uid":96536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:13:52.000Z","msg":"就連真係冇參與抗爭嘅人都受到影響<br />\n著咩衫都比人打<br />\n你地甘心比人撳撚住嚟打又唔還手咩<br />\n你地甘心啲手足受傷？<br />\n點解佢地為香港就要面對無情嘅炮火？<br />\n冇分參與遊行集會嘅都要比班野狗咬到成身傷<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">睇下啲死警犬尋晚做過啲咩</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">開槍打市民，驅散一啲穿有防護裝備嘅群眾</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">元朗就乜柒都唔理仲要放走啲野狗</span><br />\n而家已經唔到你地話唔關自己事<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">收工搭架西鐵都比人打吖</span><br />\n你地可以企出嚟保護自己同身邊嘅人<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">7.27光復元朗</span></span>"},{"pid":"d2c492232882cb62b7c64607c854f477560da513","tid":1347983,"uid":96536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:46:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fdfec8c1c054b76e3cadb4a5ca4dd1beaa878196","tid":1347983,"uid":96536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:47:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5240b178600ee633adad21121f02ce78d10d56a5","tid":1347983,"uid":96536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:47:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a2ac60f0b5e38df30b605f81abd42936c58d5fe8","tid":1347983,"uid":96536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:47:38.000Z","msg":"推"}]}